    <summary>Specifies the color primaries of a color space as defined by ITU-T H.273 (CICP).</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKColorspacePrimariesCicp` enumerates the color primary values defined in the
Coding-Independent Code Points (CICP) specification (ITU-T H.273 / ISO/IEC 23091-2).
These values are used with <xref:SkiaSharp.SKColorSpace.CreateCicp*> to create a
color space matching a specific standard.

## Examples

```csharp
var colorSpace = SKColorSpace.CreateCicp(
    SKColorspacePrimariesCicp.Rec709,
    SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp.Rec709);
```
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
